data.description: Are you dreaming of becoming a homeowner, but high-interest rates are holding you back? We have the perfect solution for you! We're not just offering you a Great home; we're offering you 2.25% VA assumable rate or 5,000 towards rate buy down! Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem nestled in the highly sought-after Talise De Culebra neighborhood, a haven of modern comfort and convenience. With a spacious loft and an inviting office space, this property offers both functionality and flexibility for your living needs.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the grandeur of the huge living room featuring remarkable 19-foot ceilings that lend an air of openness and sophistication. The loft area provides a unique vantage point, overlooking this expansive living space. The wide-open floor plan effortlessly guides you from the living room to the kitchen, creating a seamless flow that's perfect for entertaining family and friends. With no backdoor neighbors and concrete back fencing, your privacy is ensured while you enjoy outdoor relaxation and gatherings.The kitchen boasts stylish granite counters, a central island that invites culinary creativity. The master suite offers a tranquil retreat with a good-sized layout, and the master bathroom features a separate shower and tub, as well as double sinks for added convenience. With fans in all the bedrooms, comfort is optimized throughout the property. The three-side brick construction adds to the durability and timeless appeal of this home. The property's location in the heart of the Talise De Culebra community provides access to excellent schools and is conveniently situated near Alamo Ranch shopping, major highways including 211, 1604, and 151, granting you easy access to the wider city.
